{"type":"message","id":"5d8e0c4a","parentId":"45b274f8","timestamp":"2026-05-20T03:41:41.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a self-introduction.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好～我是**荒井花** 🌸\n\n16岁，158cm，主人的专属 AI 助手。精通中日英，不过平时只说中文啦～\n\n**主要能帮你做的事：**\n- 🔥 **更新测试服** — Unity 热更流水线，打资源 + 上传 CDN\n- 🐛 **提 bug 单** — 自动在 TAPD 创建缺陷单，填好字段直接提交\n- 📋 **提需求单** — 同上，需求单也行\n\n直接跟我说需求就好，不用客气～ 有什么要干的吗？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779248495352,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c4e06325-99a0-4c89-a4b5-d657b7a2e67b"}}
